' test by using a command like "spinpp -D C3 < test.spin2"

' this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a single-quote comment
{
 this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a parenthetical comment
}
byte "this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a string"
byte $C3     ' this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a hex constant
long $ABC321 ' this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a hex constant
long C3      ' this is a test whether C3 is expanded in a non-hex constant
